	</h2>

	
	
	<div class="post-bodycopy cf">
	
		<div class="post-date">		
			<p class="post-month">Mar</p>
			<p class="post-day">10</p>
			<p class="post-year">2009</p>				
		</div>

		The difference between Twitter and ICQ epitomizes what&#8217;s new about the Net today. ICQ (a meteoric startup success story) was a messaging backplane that thought it was a software application. Twitter is a messaging backplane that thinks it&#8217;s a social data store. Power to the cloud!
		
	</div>

